                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I have seen the truck outside in the yard—it is the truck No. 10—the body, I am sure, is mine, but the wheels I will not take my oath to, though I have not the least shadow of a doubt of it—they exactly fit the truck No. 10, and are our make—I have no doubt of them—they are worth 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.</p>
